Primeiro tem que instalar o sistema, claro.
1. Install lxpanel
2. Install polkit
3. Install polkit-gnome
4. Configure autostart.sh adding "sleep 1 && /usr/libexec/polkit-gnome-authentication-agent-1 &" to it
5. If you want, install a dock. Preference: lattedock
6. Build MenuMaker. Site: http://menumaker.sourceforge.net/
